originalText.text:
What I love about this place is that they bring in five star musicians to perform at a reasonable price. The food is good, the hospitality is 100% and the view to the stage from where you’re sitting is excellent. This is a beautiful welcoming place and I was floored by the stunning work Of the Metamorphosis project and the jazz ensemble, the Lotus Chamber music collective. Shunzo Ohno is the Genius behind this magnificent collective. What I admire about Ohno is the depth that he can bring from within his soul and blow it out into his trumpet , deliver it to the  ensemble as they work their talents and send it out to the audience  as perfect JAZZ…It’s enough to bring you to your knees.
He and they are truly excellence.
If you are in New York or somewhere where they are performing please call ahead for your tickets.
If I could give them 10 stars I would.
Thank you cutting edge! Bravo
